org: antoniocot
service: api-transacciones

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.12
  memorySize: 1024
  timeout: 30
  iam:
    role: arn:aws:iam::316129865556:role/LabRole
  environment:
    TRANSACTION_TABLE: TABLA-TRANSACCION

functions:
  CrearTransaccion:
    handler: CrearTransaccion.lambda_handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /transaccion/crear
          method: post
          cors: true

  EliminarTransaccion:
    handler: EliminarTransaccion.lambda_handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /transaccion/eliminar
          method: delete
          cors: true

  ObtenerTransaccion:
    handler: ObtenerTransaccion.lambda_handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /transaccion/obtener
          method: post
          cors: true

  ListarTransacciones:
    handler: ListarTransacciones.lambda_handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /transaccion/listar
          method: post
          cors: true

resources:
  Resources:
    TransaccionTable:
      Type: AWS::DynamoDB::Table
      Properties:
        TableName: ${self:provider.environment.TRANSACTION_TABLE}
        AttributeDefinitions:
          - AttributeName: cuenta_origen
            AttributeType: S
          - AttributeName: transaccion_id
            AttributeType: S
          - AttributeName: cuenta_destino
            AttributeType: S
          - AttributeName: monto
            AttributeType: N
        KeySchema:
          - AttributeName: cuenta_origen
            KeyType: HASH
          - AttributeName: transaccion_id
            KeyType: RANGE
        BillingMode: PAY_PER_REQUEST
        GlobalSecondaryIndexes:
          - IndexName: CuentaDestinoIndex
            KeySchema:
              - AttributeName: cuenta_destino
                KeyType: HASH
            Projection:
              ProjectionType: ALL
        LocalSecondaryIndexes:
          - IndexName: MontoIndex
            KeySchema:
              - AttributeName: cuenta_origen
                KeyType: HASH
              - AttributeName: monto
                KeyType: RANGE
            Projection:
              ProjectionType: ALL
